stories.headline: Nations Agree on Landmark Global Carbon Reduction Targets at COP30 Summit
stories.summary: Major economies committed to ambitious new carbon emission cuts at the UN Climate Summit, signaling a renewed global effort against climate change.

stories.headline: US Congress Passes Bipartisan AI Safety and Ethics Bill
stories.summary: The landmark legislation establishes new oversight for AI development and deployment, aiming to balance innovation with public safety and ethical concerns.

stories.headline: Emergency Summit Convenes on Escalating Gaza Humanitarian Crisis
stories.summary: International leaders meet to address the dire humanitarian situation in Gaza, seeking urgent aid delivery and pathways to de-escalation.

stories.headline: European Central Bank Hints at Future Interest Rate Cuts Amid Slowing Inflation
stories.summary: The ECB signals potential rate reductions next year, offering relief to businesses and consumers across the Eurozone as inflation eases.

stories.headline: New Dengue Fever Vaccine Shows High Efficacy in Asia Clinical Trials
stories.summary: Phase 3 clinical trials in Southeast Asia reveal a highly effective new vaccine against dengue fever, offering hope for millions at risk.
